{
  "text": "where C is an undetermined constant. There is another undetermined constant D in the psi-series which occurs for the first time in Q 2 . Not all the singularities of Lorenz are proved to be psi-series of this form. However, a few singularities were examined numerically in [CITATION_1] and were all found to be psi-series of the form given above. In addition, the locations of the singularities were determined with 10 digits of precision, which makes the Lorenz example useful for validating the numerical method described here.",
